        <title><![CDATA[SAFARI 2000 AERONET-DERIVED DIFFUSE SPECTRAL IRRADIANCE FOR EIGHT CORE SITES]]></title>

        <onlink><![CDATA[http://daac.ornl.gov/mercury_harvest/791.xml]]></onlink>
        
